high_descs: Move to the shelf below the television.
Pick up the watering can from the bottom shelf.
Turn left, then move to the tall lamp.
Turn on the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a watering can by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Walk forward and face the TV stand.
Pick up the watering can on the lower shelf.
Turn around and go to the lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Use the lamp light to examine the watering can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk over to the right side of the shelving unit the television is on.
Pick up the watering can off of the bottom shelf of the wooden shelving unit in front of you.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the tall lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the light of the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watering can in the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: move forward and locate a shelf under the television
pick up the ceramic jug
turn around and head for the standing lamp
turn on the standing lamp
anns.task_desc: turn on the lamp while with the jug

high_descs: Walk forward to the television stand on the right against the wall.
Pick up the watering can from the bottom shelf of the television stand.
Turn left and walk to the floor lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watering can by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the cabinet then turn left and take a step then turn right and walk to the tv on your right and turn to face it.
Pick up the watering can that's under the tv.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the light.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a watering can by lamplight.
